                <ab>In this letter Guru Paṇḍitarāja Raṅganātha Pauḍyāla orders the Patan <foreign>amālī</foreign> responsible for doing so to make sure that the decreed three-year term for boys performing at Patan’s Kārttika-Nāc is enforced.</ab>
